<Procedure>
<Title>To Open an Application Window</Title>
<Step>
<ItemizedList Mark="&bull;">
<ListItem Id="HIMGR.BSK.item.79">
<Para>Click the application's control in the Front Panel.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HIMGR.BSK.item.80">
<Para><Emphasis>Or:</Emphasis>
</Para>
<ItemizedList Mark="&bull;" Role="tight">
<ListItem Id="HIMGR.BSK.item.81">
<Para>From within Application Manager, click the application's icon.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HIMGR.BSK.item.82">
<Para>From within File Manager, choose an action for a selected icon.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HIMGR.BSK.item.83">
<Para>From within a terminal emulator window, type the command to start
the application.
</Para>
</ListItem>
</ItemizedList>
</ListItem>
</ItemizedList>
</Step>
</Procedure>
<Procedure>
<Title>To Close an Application Window</Title>
<Step>
<Para>Closing an application window removes it from all workspaces.
</Para>
<Caution>
<Para>Before closing an application window, save your work.
</Para>
</Caution>
</Step>
</Procedure>
<Procedure>
<Title>Mouse</Title>
<Step>
<ItemizedList Mark="&bull;">
<ListItem Id="HIMGR.BSK.item.84">
<Para>Choose Close from the application's File menu.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HIMGR.BSK.item.85">
<Para><Emphasis>Or,</Emphasis> Double-click the Window menu button (in the
upper right corner of the application's window).
</Para>
</ListItem>
</ItemizedList>
</Step>
</Procedure>
<Procedure>
<Title>Keyboard</Title>
<Step>
<ItemizedList Mark="&bull;">
<ListItem Id="HIMGR.BSK.item.86">
<Para>Press Alt+F4.
</Para>
</ListItem>
</ItemizedList>
</Step>
</Procedure>
