icons</GlossTerm>. This keeps the windows easily available and programs running in
them continue to run.</Para>
<Procedure>
<Title>Mouse</Title>
<Step>
<Para Role="indent"><InlineGraphic Remap="graphic" Entityref="WinMin"></InlineGraphic>Click the window's minimize button.</Para>
