</Para>
<ItemizedList Mark="&bull;">
<ListItem Id="HIMGR.BSK.item.94">
<Para>With your mouse, double-click the icon.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HIMGR.BSK.item.95">
<Para>With your keyboard:
</Para>
<OrderedList>
<ListItem Id="HIMGR.BSK.item.96">
<Para>With keyboard focus on the icon, press Alt+Spacebar to display the
window icon menu.</Para>
</ListItem>
