is on the Front Panel.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HIMGR.BSK.item.153">
<Para>Press the arrow keys to move the highlight to the button for the
workspace you want to display.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HIMGR.BSK.item.154">
<Para>Press Return.
</Para>
</ListItem>
</OrderedList>
</Step>
</Procedure>
<Procedure>
