</Para>
<Para><InlineGraphic Remap="graphic" Role="left" Entityref="Lock"></InlineGraphic>&newline;&empty;&newline;</Para>
</ListItem>
</ItemizedList>
<Para>To unlock your display, type your password.</Para>
<Para>&newline;&empty;&newline;</Para>
